Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H1E2090&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,X.X.X Rider is Born!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD General Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan is already proceeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting today, you're going to become king of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been half a year since I've last been to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Professor Jin's son, Jin Keisuki, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an important hostage. Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can take on us by yourself? How brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you guy's aren't human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish man! \NDo you want to be Neptune's sacrifice and die?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've chosen the path of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When these bubbles catch you, \Nyour body will turn into a skeleton and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were in Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The marine university closed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I decided to look for a part-time job in Tokyo or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But, are you okay? Why are you wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Swimming during winter, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Swimming during winter? With your clothes on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a bit cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in his hiding place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,His hiding place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor! Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When did my father move into here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like before, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke. You've got a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Scientists need to have better skills than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember saying I want to become a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:06:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid son!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does this happen every time you meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you guys were really close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, with this damn father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you get bullied in front of your future wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad taste, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're embarrased, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke. Wear this from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it. This looks girly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't oppose me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to wear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you when you came back from Okinawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about that carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That stubborn father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father wants to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be crammed in a small room and study about human engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...want to cross the seven oceans and become the world's best sailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be okay with that, Keisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...but Professor feels really lonely sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He works by himself in his university...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the only person by his side is me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Although he says stuff like that, \NI really think he's actually heartbroken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:09:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw him write letters to you many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But, now he really wants you to help with his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everyone around him thinks he's mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, why don't you help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki Ryouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a phone call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the GOD General Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...that GOD needs his, Professor Jin's knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If he refuses...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...he'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship's shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD Organization is a secret society in which opposing countries secretly joined hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...and uses modified humans to try to take over Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A secret society run by fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not helping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want revenge for my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Father, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke. Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't surprise me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why I want you to wear this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This jacket is a complete bulletproof vest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as bullets, it's also \Nresistant against fire and explosions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Professor's creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke. Starting tomorrow, you'll have a busy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A full blown fight against GOD is finally going to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he making me do these things? \NBecause I didn't help?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you and your father are in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid son...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are GOD?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're called the GOD Warfare Agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You two shall die happily together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...the only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:15:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now with the last of his remaining consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Jin used his all to perform a cell operation on Keisuke's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the Professor's final love given to his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew this day would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke. Your body isn't human anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the only way I could save your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me. You became a modified human, a Kaizorg.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaizorg?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body has the power to resist hydraulic pressure of up to 10,000 meters undersea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is "Kamen Rider X".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That island was made by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That island {\i1}is{\i0} me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The island itself is a great computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My full character and knowledge is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keitaro, the scientist, lives there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke. This is my Jin Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time you need me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll be waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come visit me at this Jin Station at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:17:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD stole my blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,With them, GOD will be a bigger devil organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to ride on this Cruiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is your Ridol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,These two are used to Set Up into \NX Rider, the Perfecter and Redizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My last wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Push the "C" switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This Jin Station is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat the evil organization GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch me, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke, with his Redizer and Perfecter, Sets Up into Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the last bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Ryouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kiriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this neckerchief for your wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In half a day it should get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Similar...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.67,0:22:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to annihilate Japan, the great organization GOD has begun to take strange actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke, betrayed by his lover and his father killed, hasn't yet healed his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Ryouko betray him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:23:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is this mysterious woman, Kiriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose, Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(194,72)}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle against GOD has just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Run, Cruiser! X Rider!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.07,0:23:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.07,0:23:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider